phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common performance/memory mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Static context | Use WeakReference |
| Inner class | Use static inner |
| No cleanup | Cleanup in onDestroy |
| Heavy ViewModel | Use lazy init |
| String concat | Use StringBuilder |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. WeakReference
private var contextRef: WeakReference<Context>? = null

// 2. Static inner class
class SafeClass

// 3. Cleanup in onDestroy
override fun onDestroy() {
    super.onDestroy()
    handler.removeCallbacks(runnable)
}

// 4. Lazy init
private val heavy by lazy { HeavyObject() }

// 5. StringBuilder
val sb = StringBuilder()

// 6. Primitive types
var sum: Int = 0
```
